[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     42[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     43[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # --- Action Space ---
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     44[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # These are the discrete actions the RL agent can recommend at each decision point.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     45[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Each maps to a specific ventilator adjustment or clinical action.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     46[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # The ordering matters: index 0 is "do nothing," higher indices are more aggressive.
